  "notes": "Proud Praxian Nomad, smart and a good leader but limited communication with local barbarians. Very skilled with kopis, better at parrying than with shield. Poor armor makes him weak against missiles. Fanatical devotion to White Bull and Yelmalio. Truth Rune means he despises lies. Geas: must challenge all Darkness creatures on sight to first blood or beyond. Gift: half damage from fire.",
